And then my little boy thought up the deep end of the ocean.

25:19.499 --> 25:20.740
Really?

25:20.760 --> 25:20.860
Yeah.

25:21.262 --> 25:22.283
then five-year-old.

25:22.303 --> 25:23.384
Isn't that great?

25:23.404 --> 25:23.744
Yeah.

25:23.764 --> 25:24.405
Great title.

25:24.805 --> 25:25.065
Yeah.

25:25.085 --> 25:28.568
I claim no credit for it, but he thought it up.

25:29.389 --> 25:32.471
This other one, the title in the dream was actually better.

25:34.093 --> 25:38.176
And how about the characters and the characters' names and their voices, all this you've heard?

25:39.017 --> 25:39.157
Uh-huh.

25:41.559 --> 25:42.019
No kidding.

25:44.782 --> 25:49.966
But if I ever, it must be, I think it must be that vitamin, you know, that vitamin now, melanin.

25:49.986 --> 25:50.226
Oh, why not?

25:50.266 --> 25:50.827
Sure.

25:50.847 --> 25:51.167
It must be it.

25:51.772 --> 25:54.797
Now, is your background Italian-American?

25:54.817 --> 25:57.321
No, I was, my married name is Allegretti.

25:57.722 --> 25:58.504
I see.

25:58.524 --> 25:59.666
My husband was Italian.

26:00.146 --> 26:00.407
Okay.

26:00.988 --> 26:04.394
And I grew up... Wait, is Misha a French?

